longBusinessSummary: Crombie invests in real estate that enriches local communities and enables long-term sustainable growth. As one of the country's leading owners, operators, and developers of quality real estate, Crombie's portfolio primarily includes grocery-anchored retail, retail-related industrial, and mixed-used residential properties in Canada's top urban and suburban markets. As at June 30, 2023, our portfolio contains 293 income-producing properties comprising approximately 18.6 million square feet, and a significant pipeline of future development projects.
